vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Barrick Investor Finally Sees Positive Return After 25 Years As Gold Hits $3,500/Oz.</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">inhauscreative</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Note: We have used Barrick to represent Barrick Gold throughout the article and any other reference to the word \"Gold\" is a reference to the commodity. This is necessary</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155447594/image_155447594.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741531-barrick-an-alternative-to-making-money-in-gold", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:32:35"}, {"id": "4741546", "title": "OPEC Update - November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Low Wide Angle Image of an Off-Shore Oil Rig at Dusk Off the Coast of Huntington Beach with Copy Space\" data-id=\"1455527715\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jeremy Poland</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By D. Coyne</em></p> <p>The <a href=\"https://www.opec.org/opec_web/en/publications/338.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">OPEC Monthly Oil Market Report</a> (MOMR) for November 2024 was published recently. The last month reported in most of the OPEC charts that follow is October 2024 and output reported for OPEC nations is crude</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741546-opec-update-november-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:22:00"}, {"id": "4741540", "title": "Eurozone Unemployment Remains At Historic Low", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Job search, headhunting and recruitment process concept. Icons for skills, education, qualification, interview and application inside gears. Hiring and human resources workflow automation.\" data-id=\"1355612139\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"574px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NicoElNino/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/bert-colijn/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bert Colijn</a></em></p> <p>The labour market is still exerting upward pressure on inflation. Wage growth reached its highest-ever level in the third quarter and unemployment remained at its historic low at the start of the fourth</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355612139/image_1355612139.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741540-eurozone-unemployment-remains-historic-low", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:15:00"}, {"id": "4741526", "title": "BuzzFeed: This Rally Can Last Longer", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"BuzzFeed office in NYC\" data-id=\"1036116888\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3817px\" height=\"2736px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Roman Tiraspolsky</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>After a disastrous SPAC merger in 2021, <b>BuzzFeed, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BZFD\" title=\"BuzzFeed, Inc.\">BZFD</a></span>) has quietly surged over 300% in 2024. The company's strategic shift to use AI tools in its workflow to generate quizzes, articles, and other digital content has positioned them</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1036116888/image_1036116888.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741526-buzzfeed-this-rally-can-last-longer", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:07:53"}, {"id": "4741539", "title": "Navigating Troubled Waters: What The Surge In Bankruptcy Filings Means For The Economy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Piggy bank in pieces\" data-id=\"1222778351\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5086px\" height=\"3509px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The financial landscape is showing signs of strain as bankruptcy filings surge, with businesses and consumers alike feeling the pressure of shifting economic conditions. Despite Federal Reserve rate cuts aimed at stabilizing the market, historical patterns suggest that monetary policy</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1222778351/image_1222778351.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741539-navigating-troubled-waters-what-the-surge-in-bankruptcy-filings-means-for-the-economy", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:04:00"}, {"id": "4741524", "title": "Medtronic: Guidance Raised, Solid Dividend, Shares Still A Bargain", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medtronic office in Silicon Valley, Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1689196299\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_1689196299.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Health Care sector has taken it on the chin in the past month. President-elect Trump's win, and subsequent pick to lead the Department of Health and Human Services (HHS), was met with selling pressure in November across much of the pharma and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689196299/image_16